Fungsi Crawling¶

def crawling_ta_byprod(list_byprod_no, file_path, pagination_start=1,):
    data = {"penulis": [], "judul": [], "pembimbing_pertama": [], "pembimbing_kedua": [], "abstrak_id": [], "abstrak_en": [], "prodi":[]}
    
    
    # Jika file masih kosong kasih header
    file_is_empty = not os.path.exists(file_path) or os.stat(file_path).st_size == 0
    with open(file_path, "a", newline="", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        writer = csv.writer(f)
        # tulis header hanya jika file kosong
        if file_is_empty:
            writer.writerow(["penulis", "judul", "pembimbing_pertama", "pembimbing_kedua",
                            "abstrak_id", "abstrak_en", "prodi"])

    url_byprod = "https://pta.trunojoyo.ac.id/c_search/byprod/"

    for no_prod in list_byprod_no:
        for i in range(pagination_start,1000): # tiap url: 1-1000 paginasi

            # for t in range(1,4):
            #     time.sleep(1)
            #     print(t,'.. ', end='')

            url_paginasi = url_byprod + no_prod + '/' + str(i)
            print(f"{url_paginasi}: paginasi {i} --",end="")

            # requests tiap paginasi
            response = requests.get(url_paginasi)
            response.raise_for_status()

            soup = BeautifulSoup(response.content, 'html.parser')

            prodi = (soup.find_all('h2')[0].get_text()).strip().split('Jurusan')[1]
            print(prodi)

            journals = soup.select("li[data-cat='#luxury']")

            if journals: # alias jika journals != []: maka lanjut lihat semua detail


                # tiap paginasi: 1-10 jurnal
                for j in journals:
                    # print('\t',end='')
                    # for t in range(1,4):
                    #     time.sleep(1)
                    #     print(t,'.. ', end='')

                    # requests tiap detail/selengkapnya sebuah skripsi
                    response_selengkapnya = requests.get(j.select_one('a.gray.button')['href'])
                    response.raise_for_status()

                    soup_selengkapnya = BeautifulSoup(response_selengkapnya.content, 'html.parser')

                    isi = soup_selengkapnya.select_one('div#content_journal')

                    judul = isi.select_one('a.title').text
                    print(f"\tjudul: {judul[:10]}...")

                    penulis = isi.select_one('span:contains("Penulis")').text.split(' : ')[1]

                    pembimbing1 = isi.select_one('span:contains("Dosen Pembimbing I")').text.split(' : ')[1]
                    pembimbing2 = isi.select_one('span:contains("Dosen Pembimbing II")').text.split(' :')[1]

                    abstracts = isi.select('p[align="justify"]')

                    ab_id = abstracts[0].text
                    ab_en = abstracts[1].text

                    data["penulis"].append(penulis)
                    data["judul"].append(judul)
                    data["pembimbing_pertama"].append(pembimbing1)
                    data["pembimbing_kedua"].append(pembimbing2)
                    data["abstrak_id"].append(ab_id)
                    data["abstrak_en"].append(ab_en)
                    data["prodi"].append(prodi)


                    with open(file_path, "a", newline="", encoding="utf-8") as f:
                        writer = csv.writer(f)
                        writer.writerow([penulis, judul, pembimbing1, pembimbing2, ab_id, ab_en, prodi])


                    # test
                    # print(f"{judul}\n{penulis} -- {pembimbing1} -- {pembimbing2} -- {prodi}\n{ab_id}\n\n\n{ab_en}")

            else: # jika journals == []: berhenti (tidak sampai 1000) lanjut ke url byprod/d selanjutnya
                break
        pagination_start = 1
    return data

categories = ['health', 'politics', 'science', 'technology',]
dictRespAllCat = {'health':[], 'politics':[], 'science':[], 'technology':[],}
for cat in categories:
    page = None
    print(f"---{cat}---")
    for i in range(2): # ulang 2 kali karena dipecah jadi 2x300 hasil
        print(f"{i+1}- page: {page}")
        resp = api.news_api(category=cat,scroll=True,language='en',max_result=300,page=page)
        page = resp['nextPage']
        
        # tambahkan resp ke categorinya masing"
        dictRespAllCat[cat].append(resp)
    
    print("\n\n\n")
    
    # simpan setiap selesai 1 cat
    with open(f'./json/resp-{cat}.json', 'a', encoding='utf-8') as f:
        json.dump(dictRespAllCat[cat], f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=4)
        
        print(f"=== dictRespAllCat[{cat}] dengan panjang {len(dictRespAllCat[cat])} tersimpan di ./json/resp-{cat}.json ===")

categories = ['business','ed', 'health', 'politics', 'science', 'technology',]
dataAllCatLumped = {'article_id':[], 'title':[], 'description':[] , 'content':[], 'category':[], 'link':[], 'language':[]}
# get data from json
for cat in categories:
    with open(f'./json/resp-{cat}.json', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:
        dataCat = json.load(f) # data 1 kategori (= 1 file)
    for batch in dataCat:
        for article in batch['results']:
            dataAllCatLumped['article_id'].append(article['article_id'])
            dataAllCatLumped['title'].append(article['title'])
            dataAllCatLumped['description'].append(article['description'])
            dataAllCatLumped['content'].append(article['content'])
            dataAllCatLumped['category'].append(cat)
            dataAllCatLumped['language'].append(article['language'])
            dataAllCatLumped['link'].append(article['link'])

dfAllCatLumped = pd.DataFrame(dataAllCatLumped)
dfAllCatLumped.to_csv('./csv/berita-online-6-kategori.csv')

from urllib.parse import urljoin, urlparse

artikel_links = ["https://pertanian.trunojoyo.ac.id/",
"https://pertanian.trunojoyo.ac.id/pengumuman/",
"https://pertanian.trunojoyo.ac.id/administrasi/",
"https://pertanian.trunojoyo.ac.id/fasilitas/laboratorium/",]
base_domain = "pertanian.trunojoyo.ac.id"
with open("./csv/graph_links.csv", "w", newline="", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    writer = csv.writer(f)
    writer.writerow(["link_asal", "link_keluaran"])  # header

    for asal in artikel_links:
        try:
            resp_link = requests.get(asal, verify=False, timeout=10)  # verify=False karena SSL
            soup_link = BeautifulSoup(resp_link.content, "html.parser")

            for a in soup_link.find_all("a", href=True):
                keluar = urljoin(asal, a["href"])  # buat absolute URL
                domain = urlparse(keluar).netloc

                if base_domain in domain:
                    writer.writerow([asal, keluar])

        except Exception as e:
            print(f"Gagal ambil {asal}: {e}")

import csv
import networkx as nx
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# buat directed graph
G = nx.DiGraph()

# baca CSV
with open("./csv/graph_links.csv", newline="", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    reader = csv.reader(f)
    next(reader)  # skip header

    for row in reader:
        no, asal, keluar = row
        G.add_edge(asal, keluar)  # tambahkan edge (arah dari asal ke keluar)

# ukuran figure
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 12))

# layout graph
pos = nx.spring_layout(G, k=0.5, seed=42)  # posisi node otomatis

# gambar nodes dan edges
nx.draw_networkx_nodes(G, pos, node_size=500, node_color="skyblue")
nx.draw_networkx_edges(G, pos, arrowstyle="->", arrowsize=15, edge_color="gray")
nx.draw_networkx_labels(G, pos, font_size=8, font_family="sans-serif")

plt.title("Graph Hyperlink Antar Artikel", fontsize=16)
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()
import csv import networkx as nx import matplotlib.pyplot as plt # buat directed graph G = nx.DiGraph() # baca CSV with open("./csv/graph_links.csv", newline="", encoding="utf-8") as f: reader = csv.reader(f) next(reader) # skip header for row in reader: no, asal, keluar = row G.add_edge(asal, keluar) # tambahkan edge (arah dari asal ke keluar) # ukuran figure plt.figure(figsize=(12, 12)) # layout graph pos = nx.spring_layout(G, k=0.5, seed=42) # posisi node otomatis # gambar nodes dan edges nx.draw_networkx_nodes(G, pos, node_size=500, node_color="skyblue") nx.draw_networkx_edges(G, pos, arrowstyle="->", arrowsize=15, edge_color="gray") nx.draw_networkx_labels(G, pos, font_size=8, font_family="sans-serif") plt.title("Graph Hyperlink Antar Artikel", fontsize=16) plt.axis("off") plt.show()
